All of a sudden a protoforms spark went offline in the bowels of the 
ship, but a force rose up from the Inferno itself to resurrect the 
protoform with a pure black spark.  The Predicon chip made it 
blacker.  This bot a a thirst for power even greater than his 
counterparts.  He had to take it from his counterpart.  He got out and 
started smashing thing in an attempt to crashland the ship near the 
other bot.
